---
title: Teriyaki Pork Stir-fry with mushrooms and pak choi
description: Teriyaki is a sweet, tangy sauce with umami aplenty. Much like the thick, tasty udon noodles and crunchy pak choi that also appear in this dish, teriyaki is a staple in Japanese cuisine.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220921_R12_W46_IE_IEXQCLP0105-1_KB_Main_high-2fef1937.jpg
